            </div>

                

            </div><!-- end .article-body__top-notes -->
        
                    

<div class="highlights">
    <h3 class="highlights__heading">Reporting Highlights</h3>
    <ul class="highlights__list">
                    <li class="highlights__highlight"><span class="highlights__subheading">Influencers: </span> Nevada lobbyists with little experience in green tech repeatedly got government contracts on the promise their startup, NZero, could track carbon output in real time.</li>
            <li class="highlights__highlight"><span class="highlights__subheading">Not as Promised: </span> With one exception, the carbon tracking platform didn’t work as described. That, however, hasn’t prevented the firm from securing even more government contracts.</li>
            <li class="highlights__highlight"><span class="highlights__subheading">Opportunity Cost: </span> Some state officials opposed the spending, citing a years-old list of less-showy energy efficiency projects, like changing light bulbs, that haven&#039;t been funded.</li>
            </ul>
    <p class="highlights__disclaimer">
        These highlights were written by the reporters and editors who worked on this story. <span id="survey-placeholder"></span>
    </p>
</div>

<script>
