    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/article/georgia-voter-registration-cancellation-portal-mtg-raffensperger">
                                    Marjorie Taylor Greene’s and Brad Raffensperger’s Voter Registrations Targeted in Georgia’s New Online Portal
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            Days after Georgia Democrats warned that the state’s new online portal for canceling voter registrations could be abused, officials have confirmed misuse attempts — including efforts to cancel the registrations of prominent Republicans.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/doug-bock-clark">Doug Bock Clark</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-08-03EDT19:35">Aug. 3, 7:35 p.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

